</p><p>
<h2>Software and hardware release</h2>

</p><p>
You can download a prototype release of the CodeBlue software and
hardware description files here:
<blockquote>
<b>
<a href="http://www.eecs.harvard.edu/~mdw/proj/codeblue/release/">http://www.eecs.harvard.edu/~mdw/proj/codeblue/release</a>
</b>
</blockquote>

</p><p>
We have also created a public mailing list for users of the CodeBlue
software. Use this list for questions, comments, and discussion about
the system as well as to receive notification of updates. To
subscribe, visit this page:
<blockquote>
<b>
<a href="https://www.eecs.harvard.edu/mailman/listinfo/codeblue-users">https://www.eecs.harvard.edu/mailman/listinfo/codeblue-users</a>
</b>
</blockquote>
</p><p>

